tooltip.value: Use instead of a Commission % OR use it IN ADDITION TO a % if Agent charges a transaction fee to the client.  For example, the commission could be 3% PLUS a Transaction Fee to the Client in the amount of $499.  $499 would go here as well as a %.

tooltip.name: Info Icon
tooltip.value: An amount paid to the Firm in addition to Split %.  This amount is usually covered as an additional charge to the client (i.e. Commission + Admin Fee).
